  docs/functional-spec.md:61:The harness uses a single coordinates filter `-Pcoordinates=` accepting `all`, `group:artifact`, `group:artifact:version`, or shard `k/n`. It also exposes authoring helpers (`generateMetadata`, `splitTestOnlyMetadata`, `fixTestNativeImageRun`, `addTestedVersion`, `fetchExistingLibrariesWithNewerVersions`), reporting tasks (`jacocoTestReport`, `generateDynamicAccessCoverageReport`, `generateLibraryStats`, `analyzeExternalLibraryDynamicAccess`, `listTopCoordinatesByMetric`, `generateTopCoordinatesByMetricMatrix`), and the `package` release task. Its task groups and the Gradle harness that delegates `-Pcoordinates=` to per-coordinate sub-builds are specified in §TCK-test-harness; the test sources it drives in §TESTS-suite. The full task reference lives in [DEVELOPING.md](DEVELOPING.md).
